// üöÄ Safe User Avatar (‡πÅ‡∏™‡∏î‡∏á‡∏ï‡∏±‡∏ß‡∏≠‡∏±‡∏Å‡∏©‡∏£‡∏¢‡πà‡∏≠‡∏≠‡∏¢‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á‡πÄ‡∏î‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ß)
const UserAvatar = ({ name, size = "md" }) => {
  const sizeClasses = {
    sm: "w-6 h-6 text-[10px]",
    md: "w-8 h-8 text-xs",
    lg: "w-10 h-10 text-sm"
  };

  return (
    <div className={`${sizeClasses[size]} rounded-full bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center font-bold border border-blue-100 shadow-sm shrink-0 select-none`} title={name}>
      {name ? name.charAt(0) : '?'}
    </div>
  );
};

const DashboardCard = ({ title, children, icon, iconBgColor = 'bg-gray-100', iconTextColor = 'text-gray-600', className = '' }) => (
  <div className={`bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 flex flex-col h-full ${className}`}>
    <div className="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
      <div className={`p-2 rounded-lg ${iconBgColor} ${iconTextColor}`}>{icon}</div>
      <h3 className="text-gray-400 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wider">{title}</h3>
    </div>
    {children}
  </div>
);

const ProjectHealthCard = ({ projects }) => {
  const activeProjects = projects.filter(p => p.project_status !== 'Cancelled');
  const total = projects.length;
  const onPlan = activeProjects.filter(p => p.status === 'On Plan').length;
  const delayed = activeProjects.filter(p => p.status === 'Delay').length;
  const completed = projects.filter(p => p.status === 'Completed').length;
  const cancelled = projects.filter(p => p.project_status === 'Cancelled').length;
  const onHold = projects.filter(p => p.project_status === 'Hold').length;

  return (
    <DashboardCard title="Project Health" icon={<Briefcase size={20}/>} iconBgColor="bg-blue-100" iconTextColor="text-blue-600">
      <div className="flex flex-col gap-2">
        <div className="flex justify-between items-center border-b pb-2 mb-2">
          <span className="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800">{total}</span>
          <span className="text-sm text-gray-400">Total Projects</span>
        </div>
        <div className="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-sm font-medium">
          <div className="flex items-center gap-2 text-emerald-600"><CheckCircle size={16} /> On Plan: {onPlan}</div>
          <div className="flex items-center gap-2 text-red-600"><AlertCircle size={16} /> Delay: {delayed}</div>
          <div className="flex items-center gap-2 text-orange-600"><PauseCircle size={16} /> Hold: {onHold}</div>
          <div className="flex items-center gap-2 text-purple-600"><Check size={16} /> Completed: {completed}</div>
          <div className="flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-500 col-span-2"><XCircle size={16} /> Cancelled: {cancelled}</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </DashboardCard>
  );
};

const FinancialOverviewCard = ({ totalBudget, totalForecastRevenue, actualRevenue }) => {
  const achievementPercent = totalForecastRevenue > 0 ? (actualRevenue / totalForecastRevenue) * 100 : 0;

  return (
    <DashboardCard title="Financial Overview" icon={<Coins size={20}/>} iconBgColor="bg-orange-100" iconTextColor="text-orange-600">
      <div className="flex flex-col gap-3">
        <div>
          <span className="text-sm text-gray-400 block mb-1">Total Budget (THB)</span>
          <span className="text-xl font-bold text-gray-600">‡∏ø{(totalBudget / 1000000).toLocaleString(undefined, { maximumFractionDigits: 1 })} M</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span className="text-sm text-gray-400 block mb-1">Actual Revenue (Earned)</span>
          <span className="text-3xl font-bold text-emerald-600">‡∏ø{actualRevenue.toLocaleString(undefined, { maximumFractionDigits: 0 })}</span>
        </div>
        <div className="mt-2">
          <div className="flex justify-between items-center text-xs text-gray-500 mb-1">
            <span>Achievement (Target: ‡∏ø{totalForecastRevenue.toLocaleString(undefined, { maximumFractionDigits: 0 })})</span>
            <span className="font-bold text-emerald-600">{Math.min(100, achievementPercent).toFixed(1)}%</span>
          </div>
          <div className="w-full bg-gray-100 rounded-full h-2">
            <div 
              className="bg-emerald-500 h-2 rounded-full transition-all duration-500" 
              style={{ width: `${Math.min(100, achievementPercent)}%` }}
            ></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </DashboardCard>
  );
};

const BUMixCard = ({ buData }) => {
  const COLORS = ['#22C55E', '#F97316', '#EAB308', '#8B5CF6', '#06B6D4', '#EC4899', '#6B7280'];
  const totalRevenue = buData.reduce((sum, val) => sum + val.value, 0);

  return (
    <DashboardCard title="Revenue by BU" icon={<PieChart size={20}/>} iconBgColor="bg-purple-100" iconTextColor="text-purple-600" className="md:col-span-1">
      <div className="flex items-center justify-between h-full -mt-2">
        <div className="w-1/2 h-[150px]">
          <ResponsiveContainer width="100%" height="100%">
            <PieChart>
              <Pie
                data={buData}
                dataKey="value"
                nameKey="name"
                innerRadius={50}
                outerRadius={70}
                paddingAngle={2}
              >
                {buData.map((entry, index) => (
                  <Cell key={`cell-${index}`} fill={COLORS[index % COLORS.length]} />
                ))}
              </Pie>
              <RechartsTooltip formatter={(value) => `‡∏ø${value.toLocaleString(undefined, { maximumFractionDigits: 0 })}`} />
            </PieChart>
          </ResponsiveContainer>
        </div>
        <div className="w-1/2 flex flex-col gap-1.5 text-xs">
          {buData.map((entry, index) => (
            <div key={entry.name} className="flex justify-between items-center">
              <div className="flex items-center gap-2">
                <span className="w-2 h-2 rounded-full" style={{ backgroundColor: COLORS[index % COLORS.length] }}></span>
                <span className="text-gray-700 font-medium">{entry.name}</span>
              </div>
              <span className="font-bold text-gray-800">
                {totalRevenue > 0 ? (entry.value / totalRevenue * 100).toFixed(0) : 0}%
              </span>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </DashboardCard>
  );
};

